===Adjective===
'''morbid'''

# of, or relating to [[disease]]
# [[unhealthy]] or [[unwholesome]], especially [[psychologically]]
# suggesting the [[horror]] of [[death]]; [[macabre]] or [[ghoulish]]
# [[grisly]] or [[gruesome]]

